Thomas Craig (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thomas_Craig_(actor) 0 Thomas Craig (born Craig Thompson; 4 December 1962) is an English actor. He is known for his roles in Murdoch Mysteries, Where the Heart Is, Hidden, Coronation Street, and The Navigators. Thomas_Craig ( born Craig_Thompson ; 4_December_1962 ) is an_English_actor .
